channel.description:

A brief break from my more upbeat stuff and album releases. Here’s something seasonal and smooth to bump in the whip down the highway or somethin’.

Also my first attempt at mastering. Drop some feedback in here if you wish, thanks

item.title: Tornait - Winter Dreams [Hip-Hop, Lo-Fi]
item.dc:creator: Dadmother
item.description:
Daaaaamn, this is a smooth, sexy track. I feel like my favorite holiday drink just got a little twisted with this track I normally am kind of a stickler when it comes to such a prevalent ducker, but this is one of those times where it really lends to the track. Great atmosphere, amazing textures, excellent mastering, and a SERIOUS winter vibe in this track. Like I’m ice cold and toasty all at the same time. Very well done!

Read full topic
